Safety notice: SAILSAFE is an experimental autonomous surface vehicle project
involving high-current batteries, brushless motors and propulsion hardware.
The software and hardware designs are provided for educational and reference
purposes only, without any guarantee of safety or fitness. Building, powering
or operating this system is done entirely at your own risk. Always use
appropriate physical safety measures (fusing, manual power cut-off, tethered
testing and direct supervision).
